descriptionHtml:
A simple re-texture for the Triss Armour featuring a corset.  You will need to download another mod containing the meshes for the armour (found: [url=http://skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=4708&navtag=file/images.php?id=4708&tab=3]here[/url] or [url=http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=5135]here[/url])

Just copy the textures folder over and you\'re good to go.



Thanks to:

CD Projekt
Fraper (the original [url=http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=5135]Triss Outfit for TES Skyrim[/url] upload)
BaronDavid (For the texture used on the corset: [url=http://skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=2674]Improved NPC Clothing - High Res[/url])
Psyke23 ([url=http://skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=4708&navtag=file/images.php?id=4708&tab=3]Triss Armor Retextured[/url])
author: AGrinderZombie
